data.description: OWNER MOTIVATED! Welcome home! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bath residence is a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Situated on a desirable corner lot. NO HOA/CDD. No Flood Zone! Architecture Shingle Roof 2017, HVAC 2018, Water Heater 2019, Clean 4 point inspection/Wind mitigation was done not long ago!  As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by an inviting open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The spacious design is perfect for both entertaining and everyday life. One of the standout features of this home is the thoughtfully designed built-ins that adorn the living room. These custom additions provide both storage and a touch of elegance, making it a perfect place to showcase your cherished possessions or create a cozy reading nook. The four bedrooms are generously sized and provide ample space for relaxation and privacy. This home is in the perfect location, in the heart of USF Bulls Country. Less than 5 minutes from Busch Gardens and Adventure Island Water Park, 2 minutes to MOSI or Takomah Trail Park. Moments away from  Tampa's newest development of shopping and entertainment UpTown and the new Yuengling Brewery. Minutes from  University Mall, Movie theater, Hospitals, amazing local restaurants and so much more! Conveniently located between all of Tampa's interstates of I-75, I-4, and I-275, making commuting a breeze! Don't miss this fantastic opportunity to make this house your home. This home is move in ready! Schedule your showing today, your dream home awaits!
